---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To remove the particular file from the git use 
git rm file_name.ext
Note that this will also remove from the disk also

again to get back the file do
$ git restore --staged about.html
$ git restore about.html

to keep the about.html as untracked file

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To rename the file 
$ git mv important.log imp.log

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
To create the new branch and to switch my working to that branch
$ git switch -c branch_name

Now if any commit we do will be to the switched branch

To switch back to the master branch
use : git switch master
git switch branch_name
